==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Stimy
<hw>Sti"my</hw> }</mhw>.
<fld>(Golf)</fld> <def>To bring into the position of, or impede by, a
stymie.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Styphnate</ent>⟦br⟧
